## Habits

Avoid duplicate code; explore before changing; clear code over trivial comments. Python: `~/.venv` unless local memory says otherwise.

**robot/deepagent** → `~/.claude/memory/deepagent/`. **Org workflow** → `~/.claude/memory/INDEX.md` and `org-yandex.mdc`.

## Memory and self-improvement

- **memory** — `~/.claude/memory/INDEX.md`
- **self-improvement** — `~/claude-agent-instructions/`

**Instructions git:** `pull` before edits, **reconcile** after pull (`instructions-git-sync.md` § After pull), `push` after every commit. Cron pull every 10 min.

**Mandatory self-improvement:** substantive user feedback about agent behavior → **Task → self-improvement** same turn (not bare "ok"/"thanks"). See `~/.claude/CLAUDE.md`.

**Mandatory manager:** every **new substantive task** → **Task → manager** first (before planner, developer, mount, broad search). Again on difficulty. See `~/.claude/CLAUDE.md` § Mandatory manager.

